quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  26,61,"Falamma taraa aljamAAaniqala as-habu moosa innalamudrakoon"
  26,62,"Qala kalla inna maAAiya rabbeesayahdeen"
  26,63,"Faawhayna ila moosaani idrib biAAasaka albahra fanfalaqafakana kullu firqin kattawdi alAAatheem"
  26,64,"Waazlafna thamma al-akhareen"
  26,65,"Waanjayna moosa waman maAAahuajmaAAeen"
  26,66,"Thumma aghraqna al-akhareen"
  26,67,"Inna fee thalika laayatan wamakana aktharuhum mu/mineen"
  26,68,"Wa-inna rabbaka lahuwa alAAazeezu arraheem"
  26,69,"Watlu AAalayhim nabaa ibraheem"
  26,70,"Ith qala li-abeehi waqawmihi mataAAbudoon"
  26,71,"Qaloo naAAbudu asnamanfanathallu laha AAakifeen"
  26,72,"Qala hal yasmaAAoonakum ithtadAAoon"
  26,73,"Aw yanfaAAoonakum aw yadurroon"
  26,74,"Qaloo bal wajadna abaanakathalika yafAAaloon"
  26,75,"Qala afaraaytum ma kuntumtaAAbudoon"
  26,76,"Antum waabaokumu al-aqdamoon"
  26,77,"Fa-innahum AAaduwwun lee illa rabbaalAAalameen"
  26,78,"Allathee khalaqanee fahuwa yahdeen"
  26,79,"Wallathee huwa yutAAimuneewayasqeen"
  26,80,"Wa-itha maridtu fahuwayashfeen"
  26,81,"Wallathee yumeetunee thummayuhyeen"
  26,82,"Wallathee atmaAAu anyaghfira lee khatee-atee yawma addeen"
  26,83,"Rabbi hab lee hukman waalhiqneebissaliheen"
